official_title: A bill to amend the Comprehensive Employment and Training Act of 1973 to extend the coverage of certain manpower programs contained in such act to native Hawaiians.

summary.text: Extends, under the Comprehensive Employment and Training Act of 1973, the coverage of specified manpower programs contained in such Act to native Hawaiians.
